strategies: I based my answers on whether or not I had heard the name before and I made an association with it.
familiar: I rated it higher on the metrics if I was familiar with the name.
memorable: I thought it was more memorable if it was familiar or sounded unique.
unique: I rated the names I was familiar with as unique and also the names that I thought were unusual.
realistic: I thought the names were realistic if I was familiar with the name.
